OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thu 19 Mar to Sat 28 MarFIt
OL,6,Fwill quickly turn more settled
OL,7,Feverywhere, with most places
OL,8,Fpredominantly dry. Temperatures will
OL,9,Ffluctuate between being milder than
OL,10,Faverage to colder than average, so it
OL,11,Fis possible we could see some
OL,12,Fovernight frost and fog, but overall
OL,13,Fby day there should be frequent spells
OL,14,Fof pleasant spring sunshine making it
OL,15,Ffeel fine away from coasts exposed to
OL,16,Fa brisk easterly wind. How long the
OL,17,Fsettled conditions last is less
OL,18,Fcertain with some signals that showers
OL,19,F/ rain could return later in the
OL,20,Fperiod.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
